Package: nfm
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libncurses6 (>= 6.0), ffmpeg (>= 4.0)
Maintainer: nfm contributors <nfm@example.com>
Description: Flexible ncurses video converter for the terminal
 nfm is an interactive, menu-driven terminal frontend for ffmpeg,
 inspired by nano-ffmpeg. It provides a file browser, built-in and
 user-editable presets, hardware-capability detection, a real-time
 progress display, and a custom-encoding form — all navigable with
 keyboard shortcuts in a colour-coded ncurses interface.
 .
 Presets are stored as plain text files in ~/.config/nfm/presets/ so
 they can be edited with any text editor.
